text: St. John the Baptist Parish (SJBP, ) is a parish located in the U.S. state of Louisiana. As of the 2020 census, the population was 42,477. The parish seat is Edgard, an unincorporated area, and the largest city is LaPlace, which is also unincorporated. ==References== Category:1807 establishments in the Territory of Orleans Category:Acadiana
title: St. John the Baptist Parish, Louisiana
